1. Purpose

Grey M1 solver a la Foucart et al. 2016 [1607.07450].

This code needs 2 ghost cells on unigrid and 4 ghost cells with AMR.

A. Acknowledgements

This code is inspired by ZelmaniM1 by L.~Roberts, C.~D.~Ott, et al. 2016
[1604.07848]. However, no code from ZelmaniM1 is present here.
